@page "/hcoutcome"



    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            color: #222;
            line-height: 1.6;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1100px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px 0;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #ccc;
        }

            .header h1 {
                font-size: 2.5rem;
                font-weight: 600;
                margin-bottom: 10px;
                color: #222;
            }

            .header p {
                font-size: 1.1rem;
                color: #555;
            }

        /* Course Section Grid */
        .courses-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        /* Course Card */
        .course-card {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 25px;
        }

            .course-card h2 {
                font-size: 1.4rem;
                margin-bottom: 15px;
                color: #2c3e50;
                font-weight: 600;
            }

        .course-content {
            color: #444;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

            .course-content ul {
                list-style-type: disc;
                margin-left: 20px;
                margin-top: 10px;
            }

            .course-content li {
                margin-bottom: 8px;
            }

        /* Button */
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #2c3e50;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

            .btn:hover {
                background-color: #1a252f;
            }

        /* Stats Section */
        .stats-section {
            background-color: #e9e9e9;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 30px;
            margin-top: 40px;
        }

        .stats-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(180px, 1fr));
            gap: 25px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .stat-item h3 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: #2c3e50;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .stat-item p {
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            color: #444;
        }


    </style>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Army Leadership Courses</h1>
            <p>Strengthening Command, Strategy, and Service</p>
        </div>

        <div class="courses-grid">
            <div class="course-card outcome">
                <h2>
                    <span class="icon">🎯</span>
                    Course Objectives
                </h2>
                <div class="course-content">
                    <p>Our leadership programs are designed to enhance strategic military effectiveness and operational excellence:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Strengthen leadership and decision-making skills</li>
                        <li>Improve mission planning and execution</li>
                        <li>Develop strategic thinking in complex environments</li>
                        <li>Promote joint operations understanding</li>
                        <li>Advance knowledge in military tactics and logistics</li>
                        <li>Prepare officers for senior command roles</li>
                        <li>Foster inter-service collaboration</li>
                    </ul>
                    <a href="#" class="btn">Explore Leadership Objectives</a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="course-card eligibility">
                <h2>
                    <span class="icon">📋</span>
                    Eligibility Requirements
                </h2>
                <div class="course-content">
                    <p>To ensure readiness and relevance, all candidates must meet the following:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Commissioned officer of Indian Army or allied forces</li>
                        <li>Minimum 5 years of active military service</li>
                        <li>Strong performance in previous leadership roles</li>
                        <li>Recommendation from commanding officer</li>
                        <li>Basic operational planning skills</li>
                        <li>Commitment to full participation</li>
                        <li>Physical and mental fitness clearance</li>
                    </ul>
                    <a href="#" class="btn">Verify Your Eligibility</a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="course-card seminars">
                <h2>
                    <span class="icon">🎓</span>
                    Seminars & Field Exercises
                </h2>
                <div class="course-content">
                    <p>Our holistic learning programs combine theory with hands-on military exercises:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Strategy and war-gaming simulations</li>
                        <li>Joint command planning workshops</li>
                        <li>Leadership in high-stress environments</li>
                        <li>Combat readiness drills</li>
                        <li>Guest lectures by senior officers</li>
                        <li>Doctrine and operational innovation discussions</li>
                        <li>Advanced scenario-based field exercises</li>
                    </ul>
                    <a href="#" class="btn">View Event Schedule</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="stats-section">
            <div class="stats-grid">
                <div class="stat-item">
                    <h3>10,000+</h3>
                    <p>Officers Trained</p>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-item">
                    <h3>98%</h3>
                    <p>Leadership Program Success Rate</p>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-item">
                    <h3>75+</h3>
                    <p>Military Courses Delivered</p>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-item">
                    <h3>4.9/5</h3>
                    <p>Officer Satisfaction Rating</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>



